Here's a fix (you get a few pops tho):
**** don't run commands you don't understand ****
head -c 591685 Boys.mp3 > Boys-head.mp3 && tail -c 128 Boys.mp3 > Boys-tail.mp3 && xxd -s 591685 -p -c 8 Boys.mp3 | grep -e "^fffbe4" -A 119 | xxd -r -p | cat Boys-head.mp3 - Boys-tail.mp3 > Boys-fixed.mp3 && rm Boys-head.mp3 Boys-tail.mp3
